Signatures.Label: If(logical_test, true_value)
Signatures.Documentation: Checks if any one of the specified conditions are met and returns the corresponding value. If none of the conditions are met, the function returns the specified default value.

Parameters.Label: logical_test
Parameters.Documentation: A condition that results in a boolean value.

Parameters.Label: true_value
Parameters.Documentation: An expression that provides the result of If when the condition is true.

Parameters.Label: else_value
Parameters.Documentation: An expression that provides the result of If when all specified conditions are false.
